scopecontent.p:
These are twelve items, 1984-1991, consisting of
         correspondence and membership applications and data sheets,
         pertaining to new membership. Included is correspondence of 
         J. Lawrence Meem, Jr., membership
         chairman, and, 
         Stuart E. Womeldorph, Jr., membership
         secretary. There is data pertaining to the membership of the
         following men: 
         Robert S. Eads, Jr.(1991); 
         William Rockwell Griswold(1990); 
         K. Edward Lay, Jr.(1985); 
         Earl Carlton Leake(1985); 
         Robert T. Lightner, Jr.(1990); 
         Edmund Whitman Morris(1990); 
         Ed Puryear(1985); 
         William Tapscott Snead(1985); 
         Albert Darden Towe(1986); 
         Walter Scott Walls(1984); and, 
         Raoul Wheeler Wilkins(1986). There is
         also correspondence, January 25 and February 1, 1991, between 
         Stuart E. Womeldorph, Jr., membership
         secretary, and 
         Patrick J. Frank, concerning the new
         procedure for processing an applicant for membership.
